@startuml
title Workflow 全局协作图
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "StrategyEntry" as Entry
component "LifecycleWorkflow" as Lifecycle
component "MarketWorkflow" as Market
component "StateWorkflow" as State
component "SubscriptionWorkflow" as Subscription
component "EventBridge" as Bridge

Entry --> Lifecycle : on_init / on_start / on_stop
Entry --> Market : on_tick / on_bars / _process_bars
Entry --> State : _create_snapshot / _record_snapshot
Entry --> Subscription : 订阅初始化 / 重算 / 订阅操作委托
Entry --> Bridge : on_order / on_trade /\non_position / 领域事件发布

Lifecycle --> Subscription : 初始化订阅模式\n启动后重算
Lifecycle --> State : 初始快照 / 停止前保存
Market --> Subscription : rollover / timer / signal 触发
Market --> State : bar 处理后记录快照
Bridge --> Subscription : on_order / on_trade /\non_position 后重算
Bridge --> State : 通过宿主触发状态更新结果
@enduml
